<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Executioner's Hood - AC 5</strong>
<font size=-1>(<a href="/prices/item/executioners_hood.shtml">View Going Price</a>)</font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/head.shtml">Head</a><BR>
Weight: 0.2 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/bard/armour/head.shtml">BRD</a>, <a href="/monk/armour/head.shtml">MNK</a>, <a href="/paladin/armour/head.shtml">PAL</a>, <a href="/ranger/armour/head.shtml">RNG</a>, <a href="/rogue/armour/head.shtml">ROG</a>, <a href="/shadow_knight/armour/head.shtml">SHD</a>, <a href="/warrior/armour/head.shtml">WAR</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) <BR>
(STR +4) (DEX +9) </font>
<BR>
Dropped in Lower Guk by Froglok Executioner.<BR>
<BR>
Avg. Price Overall: 293pp (141 quotes)<BR>
Last 30 Days: 222pp (10 quotes)<BR>

