It might be a good item, especially considering the high dex bonus and the weight, BUT it looks ugly ! Especially on dwarfes. I have a dwarven Paladin, but it will look strange on every race (I sold it to a human Paladin).<BR>
What does it look like if u run around in full metal armor and then a helm that looks like your grandmas wintercap.<BR>
Nm, i think its a good thing for monks though as it will not look that strange on someone who is all in leather.<BR>
Personally Im happy that I was able to buy this for 400 plat and sell it for 300 and a BIBS :)</font></td></tr></table>
