<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>We're forgeting one class that can really use the bonuses provided by the hood.....the poor forsaken rogues.  These are 2 stats that are extremely important for a rogue in that most lack any significant str, and also have the hp's of a caster they can certainly use the str and the little extra boost to their dodge/parry.  Also you'll find most rouges wielding a combination of missle weapons and procing piercers which also rely on dex.  As for asthetics, well I haven't seen any rouges running around sporting a full set of plate(not only can they not use it, most can't even carry it) as well a good rouge playing in character shouldn't even be seen running around.......</font></td></tr></table>
