<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The crafted helm is not very good at all in my opinion. It depends if you go for stats, then the exec hood is best in my opinion, especially if you have a weapon with a proc, wich is DEX-dependent. If you aim for AC, go for a skull shaped barbute. The Crafted helm gives good AC, but looks ugly, and gives +5 WIS (Who needs that?), and +5 CHA, wich really is bad, since (I THINK) your taunting skill is reversly dependent on charisma. That is, the lover your charisma is, the better your tauntskill works (just a rumor, but I belevie in it). And, of course, if you are an Ogre, the Crafted helmet have a horrible apperance, you know, the 'Retard giant baby look syndrome'...</font></td></tr></table>
